Detailed Description

Dataset Slot Structure for the Dataset Table.

Description:

This structure contains meta data for a dataset. Besides the information stored in the header (see _FC_SlotHeader), this struct has a structure containing file IO info. It also knows which sequences and meshes it owns.

Todo:
?someday make fileInfo dynamically allocated -- would only save a little space at the expensse of added complexity. Unless there is dynamically allocated stuff within fileInfo. Then should probably use special free routines.
Modifications:
  • 7/17/2005 WSD moved file IO stuff out into file io modules.
